  "title": "The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya",
  "display_title": "The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya",
  "html_content": "<div class=\"mw-body-content mw-content-ltr\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin:0.5em auto; max-width:50em;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"border:none; color:#B2B7F2; font-family:'Times New Roman',Times,serif; font-size:3em; font-weight:bold; line-height:41px; padding:0 16px 0 0; vertical-align:top; width:20px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"border:none; font-size:1.2em; font-style:italic; padding:0; vertical-align:middle;\">I, with this body, am filling the role of Haruhi, as the omnipotent one with the deity-level abilities and wish-making type of manifestations.\n</td>\n<td style=\"border:none; color:#B2B7F2; font-family:'Times New Roman',Times,serif; font-size:3em; font-weight:bold; line-height:11px; padding:0 0 0 16px; vertical-align:bottom; width:20px\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"font-size:smaller; padding:8px 36px; text-align:right;\"><cite>Chris, comparing himself to Haruhi<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-anaxis_1-0\"><a href=\"#cite_note-anaxis-1\">[1]</a></sup></cite>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a class=\"image\" href=\"/cwcki/File:Haruhi.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"thumbimage\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"282\" src=\"/w/images/thumb/d/d9/Haruhi.jpg/200px-Haruhi.jpg\" srcset=\"/w/images/d/d9/Haruhi.jpg 1.5x\" width=\"200\"/></a> <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/cwcki/File:Haruhi.jpg\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Haruhi Suzumiya</div></div></div>\n<p><i><b>The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya</b></i> is an <a href=\"/cwcki/Anime\" title=\"Anime\">anime</a> series. Haruhi Suzumiya is the name of its titular character. Chris <a href=\"/cwcki/Chris_and_English\" title=\"Chris and English\">misspells her name</a> as \"Suzumia\".<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-anaxis_1-1\"><a href=\"#cite_note-anaxis-1\">[1]</a></sup><sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-2\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">[2]</a></sup><sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-3\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">[3]</a></sup> The plot revolves around Haruhi, a teenage girl who unwittingly is the god of her world. Chris watched the anime on his iPad<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-4\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">[4]</a></sup> as well as its spin-off series, <i>The Disappearance of Nagato Yuki-chan</i>.<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-5\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">[5]</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions_by_Chris\">Mentions by Chris</span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/cwcki/August_2020\" title=\"August 2020\">August 2020</a>, Chris compared himself to Haruhi while reflecting on the failings of his <a href=\"/cwcki/Love_Quest\" title=\"Love Quest\">sweetheart search</a>. He wrote that, \"And like Haruhi, [I] was unaware for the time of this OP ability of [mine], and that [I] wasn’t the type as aggressive/assertive as Haruhi to push things forward.\"<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-6\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">[6]</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/cwcki/September_2020\" title=\"September 2020\">September 2020</a>, Chris compared himself, <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/cwcki/Barbara\" title=\"Barbara\">Barbara</a>, and some <a href=\"/cwcki/Watchmen\" title=\"Watchmen\">Watchmen</a> members to characters from <i>Haruhi</i>:<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-7\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">[7]</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Chris to Haruhi, being \"the omnipotent one with the deity-level abilities and wish-making type of manifestations.\" Chris also referred to the coincidence that Haruhi is called the \"Ultra Director\" and Chris had called himself the \"Great Director\" years before.</li>\n<li>Barbara to Kyon (misspelled as \"Kion\" by Chris), being \"unspecial, yet Very Special.\" Notably in the anime, Kyon has a kissing scene with Haruhi, signifying another piece of foreshadowing for Chris's <a href=\"/cwcki/Affair_with_Mother\" title=\"Affair with Mother\">Affair with Mother</a>.<sup class=\"reference\" id=\"cite_ref-8\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">[8]</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cwcki/Lainchu\" title=\"Lainchu\">Lainchu</a> to Yuki Nagato, being \"able to reprogram certain data within the micro ness and fabrics of realities, timelines and dimensions, and so on to her great extent and skill set. Also, your respective insight to the present situations and all that.\"</li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/cwcki/Bismuth\" title=\"Bismuth\">Bismuth</a> to Itsuki Koizumi, since \"his range of abilities being something similar, yet far superior than Koizumi. And in that he has an innate sense, reasoning, logic and intelligence that makes him able to be that who has a better understanding of this body's abilities than I do.\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"/cwcki/MKRNightVee\" title=\"MKRNightVee\">MKRNightVee</a> to Mikuru Asahina, though Chris was uncertain since \"she's not exactly moe or shy, but she still has her abilities as well that surpasses that of a typical time-traveler type.\"</li></ul>\n<p>In <a href=\"/cwcki/Jail_Letter_-_4_October_2021\" title=\"Jail Letter - 4 October 2021\">Jail Letter - 4 October 2021</a> and <a href=\"/cwcki/Jail_Letter_-_18_January_2022\" title=\"Jail Letter - 18 January 2022\">Jail Letter - 18 January 2022</a>, Chris listed Haruhi as among the inhabitants of his fantasy dimension <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/cwcki/C-197\" title=\"C-197\">C-197</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-anaxis-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-anaxis_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-anaxis_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/Anaxis_DMs\" title=\"Anaxis DMs\">Anaxis DMs</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/Jail_Letter_-_4_October_2021\" title=\"Jail Letter - 4 October 2021\">Jail Letter - 4 October 2021</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/Jail_Letter_-_18_January_2022\" title=\"Jail Letter - 18 January 2022\">Jail Letter - 18 January 2022</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/File:23_Aug_20_iPad_screenshot_-_14BLC.jpg\" title=\"File:23 Aug 20 iPad screenshot - 14BLC.jpg\">File:23 Aug 20 iPad screenshot - 14BLC.jpg</a> Seen in a tab in a screenshot Chris took.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/File:20_Aug_20_iPad_screenshot_-_Pokestop_Nomination.jpg\" title=\"File:20 Aug 20 iPad screenshot - Pokestop Nomination.jpg\">File:20 Aug 20 iPad screenshot - Pokestop Nomination.jpg</a> Seen in a tab in a screenshot Chris took.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/Discord_Q%26A_2\" title=\"Discord Q&amp;A 2\">Discord Q&amp;A 2</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/cwcki/Anaxis_DMs#Ultra_Director\" title=\"Anaxis DMs\">Anaxis DMs#Ultra Director</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://haruhi.fandom.com/wiki/The_Melancholy_of_Haruhi_Suzumiya_Part_6\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://haruhi.fandom.com/wiki/The_Melancholy_of_Haruhi_Suzumiya_Part_6</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p class=\"mw-em